reviewText: I also got it just for the Johnny Depp film I'd never heard of, as I was on a Johnny Depp kick, and which turns out "Dead Man" is a totally classic existential noir-comedy !!! Excellently well cast and well written. I'm in awe of it !!! and very surprised it's not a considered a 'cult classic'.
I bought this because of the Johnny Depp movie. It is great. I got four movies for a very low price including one wonderful Johnny Depp movie that I had never even heard of thanks to Amazon.
yes,4 good movies on 2 discs,good quality also, came on time, i also liked all the films too, from echo bridge
